  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the chicken breast and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the potato, carrot, cherry, kombu cold extract, chicken broth, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 30 minutes.",
    "Stir occasionally to prevent the ingredients from sticking to the pot.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
  ],
